        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[Vitalik 解释转移 ETH ：2018 年起就不再为个人利益卖币]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>以太坊创办人 Vitalik Buterin 的地址是众人注目的焦点，链上分析平台追踪的目标，有的人也会将 Vitalik 卖出 ETH 作为利空讯号。Vitalik Buterin 在去中心化社交协议 Farcaster 的用户端平台 <a href="https://abmedia.io/vitalik-confirmed-sim-swap-attack" target="_blank" rel="noopener">warpcast</a> 上发文回应这件事。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_56_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/vitalik-explain-eth-sell#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-652f66e9893fd"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
